alloc_crate::vec::Vec::<T, A>::as_slice.doc:
Extracts a slice containing the entire vector.

Equivalent to `&s[..]`.

# Examples

```
use std::io::{self, Write};
let buffer = vec![1, 2, 3, 5, 8];
io::sink().write(buffer.as_slice()).unwrap();
```

